Manufactured by FM (Fabricaciones Militares) in Argentina, this is a "Detective"...a licensed copy of the famous Browning Hi-Power. What makes the Detective unique is that it features a shortened (4-inch) barrel and slide...making it a much more compact package for concealed carry. It has a standard sized frame and utilizes standard Hi-Power magazines (being a licensed copy, all parts are interchangeable with the Browning except those associated with the short barrel/slide). Condition is very good (low round count) with one small scatch on the slide.
